<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body style="background-color:#16B6FA;color:white;padding:20px;font-size:18px;">
    <h1>Hey <%= @user.first_name %>, </h1>
    <p>
    The team at Loraction is rooting for you as you work to reduce your
    <%= @contract.level.task.category.name %> usage!
    </p>
    <p>
    Your recent reports have been around <%= @recent.to_s + " " + @contract.level.unit.to_s %>, which is good progress on reducing your current <%= @contract.level.task.name %> <%= @contract.level.name %> from <%= @contract.initial %> to <%= @contract.target %> <%= @contract.level.unit %>.
    <% if @tip %>
    As you continue to improve, remember:
    <% end %>
    </p>
    <% if @tip %>
    <div style="
      font-size: 18px;
      width: 80%;
      padding: 10px;
      background-color: rgba(223, 228, 252, 0.29);
      border-radius: 20px;
      margin: 0px auto;
      ">
      
      <%= @tip.description %>
    </div>
    <% end %>
    
    <br>
    
    <form action= <%= @url %> , method: 'post' >
      <label for=<%= @contract.level.name %>>
        Please let us know your current <%= @contract.level.task.name %> <%= @contract.level.name %>
        (<%= @contract.level.unit %>)
      </label>
      <br>
      <input type="hidden" name='contract' value=<%= @contract.id %>>
      <input type="number" name='value' style="border: 0;
      width: 150px;
      height: 34px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      padding: 2px;
      font-size: 1.2em;">
      <input type="submit" value="Submit" style="color: white;
      cursor: pointer;
      border-radius: 5px;
      border: 0;
      width: 80px;
      height:40px;
      font-size: 1em;
      background: #ffad3f;">
    </form>
    <p>
    
    </p>
    <p style="text-align:right;">Sincerely,<br>The Loraction Team  </p>
  </body>
</html>